Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天的推理真是让人大吃一惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.70,0:00:25.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}超越常识的时间差诡计
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.20,0:00:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}用滑雪手法制造的不在场证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.80,0:00:28.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}看上去是小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.10,0:00:32.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.80,0:02:00.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}神秘温泉雪夜振袖事件（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.70,0:02:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}明日香小姐进入露天温泉是在10点左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.80,0:02:10.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}绘麻小姐去庭院里的祠堂是在10点半左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.20,0:02:14.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}两人都是被这把神刀杀害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.20,0:02:17.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}神刀是在露天温泉浴池里被发现的 就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.10,0:02:21.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}犯罪过程是先杀害了绘麻小姐然后是明日香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.10,0:02:25.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}另外 在祠堂所在的庭院里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.80,0:02:28.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}只有绘麻小姐的足迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.40,0:02:32.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}而且在通往露天温泉时必须通过的娱乐场里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}10点半以后始终有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.20,0:02:37.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}哪一个都是密室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.90,0:02:39.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}是参拜振袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}樱子小姐用参拜振袖的方法向两人复仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}樱子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}那是哪一位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}我大学时的前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}被她们俩诬陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}承担了秘密进行违禁药品交易的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}因此自杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}她们是指被杀害的明日香小姐和绘麻小姐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.60,0:03:03.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}所以 所以被前辈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.60,0:03:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真先警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}祠堂里 遗体上戴的一只耳环不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是留下的另一只
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.80,0:03:16.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}啊 那个 是名牌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.60,0:03:21.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大概那样的一只也要20万日元左右吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一对就要40万日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.80,0:03:28.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}虽然不便宜 但也不至于成为杀人的理由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.80,0:03:34.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对了 春美小姐好像也有相同款式的项坠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.60,0:03:37.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}绘麻小姐好像很不高兴看到我戴有同样的项坠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}所以我立刻就摘掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.80,0:03:44.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}还有 在绘麻小姐的上衣口袋里发现了这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}另外 现场遗留的振袖和腰带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.00,0:03:50.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}是收藏在这个旅馆储藏室里的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}一般没有上锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.70,0:03:55.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}所以任何人都可以拿出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.80,0:03:58.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}大概是凶手提前藏在现场的某处了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.70,0:04:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么 来确认一下昨晚各位的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.80,0:04:04.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}首先是惠理小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}你在9点半左右去了露天温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}10点左右出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.80,0:04:12.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}然后明日香小姐进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}是的 那以后我就回自己的房间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.60,0:04:19.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}途中遇到毛利先生他们 大家站着聊了几句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.30,0:04:25.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 当时我想邀请惠里小姐去喝一杯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.40,0:04:28.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.30,0:04:31.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}赖子小姐从9点半开始就在这里做采访内容的整理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}是的 我看到惠理小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.30,0:04:40.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}然后5分钟后 我看到绘麻小姐到后门去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那是10点半左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.10,0:04:46.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}还有其他人去后门吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没有了 谁也没去过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.30,0:04:53.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}那时 毛利先生他们四个人去了露天温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.30,0:04:57.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是 女温泉门口挂着“租出”的牌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且门也被锁上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}于是你们两位又回到了娱乐场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.80,0:05:02.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.30,0:05:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}毛利先生 入浴中发现什么奇怪的事情了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.90,0:05:08.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.50,0:05:13.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}我们听见女温泉那边有“哗啦哗啦”的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那是什么时候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}应该是10点50分左右吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.40,0:05:20.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}那不是犯案时间吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.20,0:05:21.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}但是只有“哗啦哗啦”的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}并没有听到惨叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.10,0:05:26.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}不奇怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}不是说过了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.60,0:05:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}在她发出惨叫前就已被凶手用电击枪击晕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是这样的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.20,0:05:39.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}当然是这样没错的 小鬼不要妨碍调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}兰小姐和春美小姐一直呆在娱乐场吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.90,0:05:49.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是的 我忘了摘隐形眼镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.90,0:05:53.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}回房间了一趟 大概10分钟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:54.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.40,0:05:58.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}那时候谁也没有通过娱乐场 是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.10,0:05:59.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.70,0:06:03.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}毛利先生从男温泉出来是11点左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.60,0:06:07.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}那时惠理小姐和赖子小姐在这里商谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对了 阪东先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.60,0:06:12.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}11点15分左右开始和她们在一起商谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后毛利先生他们在露天温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}发现了明日香小姐的遗体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}关于振袖般若的纸人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}最初去的时候没有掉在地上吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.10,0:06:30.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}接着在祠堂发现了绘麻小姐的遗体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}绘麻小姐为什么会去祠堂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.30,0:06:35.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个问题提得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}理由是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.90,0:06:38.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}绘麻小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}有件事想和你秘密地谈一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}今晚10点半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}在院里的祠堂等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}阪东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}不 不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我没写过这样的纸条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}你在11点15分之前没有不在场证明吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.30,0:06:57.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是 我没有杀她们两人的动机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在有动机的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}好像只有春美小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}怎么会 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.60,0:07:08.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}你因为那位自杀的前辈而对她俩心怀怨恨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}另外 在回房摘掉隐形眼镜的这段时间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你并没有不在场证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我 我没做过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不论谁是凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}不解开密室之谜的话也拿他没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.30,0:07:24.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果两人是被不同的凶器所杀害的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还好办一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}还有 凶手为什么要把现场模仿成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}如振袖般若的传说那样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.20,0:07:41.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}送来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}终于送来了 验尸报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.10,0:07:49.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}杀害两人的凶器都是那把神刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.70,0:07:50.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}如果凶器不同的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}这个问题还好办一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}果然是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.30,0:08:01.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}头巾上只有绘麻小姐的血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.40,0:08:06.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还有现场和神社祠堂等地方的人偶身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以及绘麻小姐所持的纸条上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.70,0:08:12.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}均没有查出指纹之类的与凶手有关的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.70,0:08:15.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那么 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}真的很麻烦了呢 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么都没发现吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.60,0:08:29.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}接下来是昨天举行的儿童雪橇大赛的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}让开让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}好像很开心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.00,0:08:34.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.20,0:08:37.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}孩子们啊 电视里的孩子们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}让开让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以足迹才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}渐渐搞清楚了 事情的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.90,0:09:03.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这边积雪有15厘米左右啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:26.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}顶多能够陷下去5厘米左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}15厘米和5厘米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}但是 为什么那个人要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南 你去哪儿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}稍微在周围散散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}东京一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.70,0:09:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}阪东先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.50,0:09:55.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}等等 难道说那个人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.50,0:09:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 袜子全湿透了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}快去把它烤干吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}小兰姐姐 等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.30,0:10:05.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}凶手是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}一定是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}但是 为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果那个人是凶手的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.40,0:10:21.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}又是什么时候 怎么把纸人偶放到这里来的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.20,0:10:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}刚才没有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.50,0:10:30.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}就是觉得拿在手里冷冷的 心里发毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是这么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}高木吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}是我 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.40,0:10:51.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}其实是有点事想请你调查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.70,0:10:53.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小仓先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.70,0:10:57.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}毛利叔叔说有点事想拜托您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生 真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果我的推理是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.60,0:11:07.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}那个人就一定是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}你让大家到这里集合 有什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这还用说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}当然是揭开这个案件的真相了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}您知道凶手是谁了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.80,0:11:23.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}到底是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}按顺序来说明一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.00,0:11:31.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}从绘麻小姐被杀的振袖之神的祠堂密室之谜说起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真先警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}能请你把放在浴盆上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}数码相机的电源开关打开好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.30,0:11:47.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我总觉得这个脚印有点不大对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我明白过来是在今天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个哪里不对劲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}是脚印太浅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.30,0:12:00.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}昨天白天 我到祠堂去的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.80,0:12:04.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}脚陷入雪中大约7-8厘米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为之后也一直在下雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.80,0:12:13.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}晚上10点半左右到祠堂去的绘麻小姐的靴子鞋印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.90,0:12:18.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}至少也应该有15厘米深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.00,0:12:22.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 实际上最多只有7-8厘米深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这也太浅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}原来如此 那是为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是因为脚印被压平了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}脚印被压平了 被压过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.30,0:12:37.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}我为了不让绘麻小姐的脚印被雪覆盖掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.10,0:12:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在从后门延伸到祠堂的脚印之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}盖上了浴巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.00,0:12:46.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}如果这并非是浴巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}而是木板的话又会怎样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.70,0:12:52.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}从上边走过的凶手 就能不留下脚印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.70,0:12:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而往返于后门与祠堂之间了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这么简单吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}掩人耳目的诡计有时就是这么简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}恐怕 凶手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}准备了两块一米左右的木板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.20,0:13:12.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}交替盖在绘麻小姐的脚印上走过去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.20,0:13:15.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}杀害了绘麻小姐后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.50,0:13:20.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}再用同样的方法回到了后门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.50,0:13:23.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样一来 脚印虽然会稍微变浅一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但却被保留了下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}可是 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}凶手是怎样进出后门的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊 当时并没有人经过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}凶手是从屋檐下走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}用了同样的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.00,0:13:41.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}所以才没有人看到 也没有留下脚印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}根据今天早上我所调查到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.00,0:13:46.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}从后门出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.40,0:13:49.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}右边的积雪上会留下15厘米深的脚印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}左边留下的却只有5厘米深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}也就是说 凶手是从左边过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}顺着长廊的屋檐走下去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.90,0:14:03.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}到了某个地方积雪又开始变厚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那…那么 那是哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}就是你的房间前面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}明智惠理小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}惠理老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.10,0:14:20.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}昨天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.20,0:14:23.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}惠理小姐在明日香小姐入浴之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}离开了露天温泉 回到了自己的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}用刚才的方法 从后门走到祠堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.80,0:14:34.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把事先以阪东先生的名义叫出来的绘麻小姐给杀害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.20,0:14:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的确 用那种方法我是能杀了绘麻小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 要杀明日香小姐却是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}的确 建在峭壁半山腰的这座露天温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.00,0:14:49.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}用同样的方法是行不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的确如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.30,0:14:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}可是当时并没有人经过娱乐场啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.80,0:14:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.90,0:14:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}明日香小姐是在绘麻小姐之前被杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.60,0:15:06.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}惠理小姐用电击枪将明日香小姐击晕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后脱掉明日香小姐的衣物后把她杀害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}接着把尸体裹上预先藏好的腰带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}一起扔进了温泉浴池里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.10,0:15:16.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}恐怕 神刀是在前一天的晚上事先偷走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.00,0:15:17.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.70,0:15:20.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}如果绘麻小姐是在明日香小姐之后被杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.00,0:15:25.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}神刀和沾血的头巾又为什么会在温泉这里被发现的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}那个纸人偶也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.80,0:15:31.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}那是用干冰制造的机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}利用小块干冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.70,0:15:38.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把人偶固定在天花板的缝隙里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果事先计算过干冰挥发所需要时间的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.60,0:15:45.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}就可以在任何时候 让人偶落下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以人偶才是冰凉冰凉的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.60,0:15:52.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}惠理小姐拜托老板每天都给她买蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是为了弄到干冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.60,0:15:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}纸人偶倒是这样就可以解释清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是神刀和头巾又怎么解释呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我在10点半之后可没去过女温泉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.50,0:16:08.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}不到这里来 也可以让它们出现在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在就来实际演练一遍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.00,0:16:35.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}这木板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.10,0:16:40.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}是从峭壁之上的惠理小姐的房间滑下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请大家想象一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.50,0:16:46.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}用来杀害绘麻小姐的神刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沾有绘麻小姐血迹的头巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}用这个方法的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.20,0:16:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}就算不出房间也能让它们出现在女温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}毛利先生你们在入浴的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}听到的“哗啦哗啦”的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}就是木板滑下来掉到水中的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}惠理小姐就是用了这个手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}让我们对行凶的顺序产生错误的判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}从而让她的不在场证明得以成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}那两块关键的木板又到哪里去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生 我拿来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.80,0:17:18.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.00,0:17:23.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}是储藏室里其他的腰带 我把它们给冻得硬梆梆的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}用水把腰带浸湿后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.40,0:17:28.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}放在室外一个晚上的时间就会被冻成像冰块一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.20,0:17:32.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她就是利用了被冰冻的腰带来代替了这两块木板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是吗 既然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}掉进温泉里的话 腰带就会恢复原状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:45.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}浴池里的遗体旁漂浮着两条腰带会被人怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.20,0:17:48.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因此 她就在浴池里放了很多条腰带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.20,0:17:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在祠堂里也铺上了很多件振袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}模仿振袖般若的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.40,0:17:57.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}就是为了隐藏这个手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.30,0:18:04.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是精彩之极的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}可你有什么证据吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.80,0:18:10.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请你让大家看看你的脚底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}请你务必让大家看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}抱歉了 惠理老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.90,0:18:27.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好像是因为踩到了什么尖的东西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.40,0:18:30.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}不 这就是你杀害绘麻小姐的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.10,0:18:34.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}踩到了她掉落的耳环而留下的伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}昨晚 在进行现场保护的那段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}我让大家聚集在客厅里等候的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为惠理小姐说让大家坐下来比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.80,0:18:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}就改到大厅去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.00,0:18:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}惠理小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.20,0:18:54.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}当时你右脚上的伤口还流着血吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.50,0:18:58.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以你才不愿意去必须脱掉拖鞋的客厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你有什么证据证明这个伤口是那只耳环所伤吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不见了的那只耳环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}被我给找到了 看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.80,0:19:07.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}一只就值20万日元的名牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.90,0:19:13.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}只要在这上面检验出有她的血迹 就是证据了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}竟然 被你给找到了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.80,0:19:24.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其实这是 找春美小姐借的项链
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.20,0:19:36.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是我输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是我杀了她们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.20,0:19:51.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为什么 要做这样毫无意义的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.40,0:19:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}惠理老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.90,0:19:56.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}不是惠理 是智惠理老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你隐瞒了你的真名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.60,0:20:02.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为“明”这个姓实在是太少见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.20,0:20:05.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}所以大家都把“明 智惠理”误当成“明智 惠理”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.70,0:20:09.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我让警视厅的熟人调查过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.90,0:20:10.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}智惠理小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.50,0:20:16.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}你就是那位自杀了的铃鹿樱子小姐的亲姐姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}惠理老师是樱子小姐的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.60,0:20:24.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}自幼因为火灾失去了父母的你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.30,0:20:28.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只有妹妹樱子小姐被铃鹿家收养了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我会说出一切的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}妹妹自杀的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}我在波士顿学习写小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.10,0:20:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}被告知她的死讯 是一年之后的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}柔弱的樱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.10,0:20:47.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}居然因为被怀疑和违禁药物的贩卖有关就自杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.90,0:20:50.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我真是既后悔 又怜惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.80,0:20:55.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为什么一点都不和我商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是她姐姐呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.10,0:21:00.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}她是我唯一的亲人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.50,0:21:03.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我无法饶恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}樱子太悲惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.60,0:21:09.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}然后 以这次的工作为由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.00,0:21:14.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我假装若无其事找到大学同班的赖子小姐叫来了那两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.70,0:21:20.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以模仿振袖般若的复仇传说向她们复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.20,0:21:25.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样 樱子小姐就会开心了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.00,0:21:30.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这次采访的三个人里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.60,0:21:34.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}唯一一个对樱子小姐信赖理解的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.00,0:21:37.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}深津春美小姐如果没来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.70,0:21:41.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}我就不会知道你妹妹自杀的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.40,0:21:43.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就不会怀疑到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}樱子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.00,0:21:50.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}简直就像为了劝解想要犯罪的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.80,0:21:55.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}让春美小姐和你 相遇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}春美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.80,0:22:01.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}如同被般若附身的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.10,0:22:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}完全没有感受到樱子小姐的心意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.50,0:23:43.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我怎么会在这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.30,0:23:46.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不妙的兆头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.20,0:23:48.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.30,0:23:50.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.00,0:23:53.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}你就慢慢泡着温泉休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.30,0:24:04.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一定是问了保险箱的密码吧 看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.40,0:24:09.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}实际上凶手不但让社长给留下了死亡讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.20,0:24:12.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且还让保险箱的大门也敞开着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.10,0:24:16.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样一来 可疑的就是发现案发现场的四个职员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.80,0:24:18.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这话什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.90,0:24:23.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}不 沉睡的小五郎站在弱者的一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.50,0:24:25.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.00,0:24:28.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}谁的推理秀（前篇）
